CREATE OR REPLACE TABLE `narvar-data-lake.return_insights_base.tmp_product_insights_updates_2025-11-24` AS (
            WITH affected_items AS (
                -- Get unique item identifiers from the updates table
                SELECT DISTINCT
                    retailer_moniker,
                    shopify_domain,
                    order_date,
                    order_checkout_locale,
                    order_item_product_id,
                    order_item_description,
                    order_item_name,
                    order_item_sku,
                    order_item_vendor,
                    order_item_size,
                    order_item_color,
                    order_item_product_type,
                    order_item_variant_id,
                    order_item_variant_title, 
                    return_outcome
                FROM `narvar-data-lake.return_insights_base.tmp_order_item_details_2025-11-24`
            )
            -- Reaggregate all records for the affected items
            SELECT
                r.retailer_moniker,
                r.shopify_domain,
                DATE(r.order_date) AS order_date,
                r.order_checkout_locale,
                r.order_item_product_id,
                r.order_item_description,
                r.order_item_name,
                r.order_item_sku,
                r.order_item_vendor,
                r.order_item_size,
                r.order_item_color,
                r.order_item_product_type,
                r.order_item_variant_id,
                r.order_item_variant_title,
                r.return_outcome,
                
                `narvar-data-lake.return_insights_base.histogram`(ARRAY_AGG(r.item_return_reason IGNORE NULLS LIMIT 10)) AS return_reason_summary,
                `narvar-data-lake.return_insights_base.histogram`(ARRAY_AGG(r.item_child_return_reason IGNORE NULLS LIMIT 10)) AS child_return_reason_summary,
                `narvar-data-lake.return_insights_base.histogram`(ARRAY_AGG(r.return_method_id IGNORE NULLS LIMIT 10)) AS return_method_summary,

                COUNT(DISTINCT r.cdp_pii_hash) AS num_customers,
                COUNT(DISTINCT r.order_number) AS num_orders,
                COUNT(DISTINCT r.return_order_number) AS num_return_orders,
                COUNT(DISTINCT r.rma_number) AS num_rmas,
                COUNT(DISTINCT IF(r.return_outcome = 'Refund to Original Payment', r.rma_number, NULL)) AS num_refunds,
                COUNT(DISTINCT IF(r.return_outcome = 'Exchanges & Shop Now', r.rma_number, NULL)) AS num_exchanges,
                COUNT(DISTINCT IF(r.return_outcome = 'Gift Cards', r.rma_number, NULL)) AS num_gift_cards,
                COUNT(DISTINCT IF(r.is_shop_now_return, r.rma_number, NULL)) AS num_shop_now_returns,
                SUM(GREATEST(r.order_item_quantity, r.order_shipped_item_quantity)) AS num_order_items,
                SUM(r.return_item_quantity) AS num_return_items,
                SUM(if(r.return_outcome = 'Refund to Original Payment', r.return_item_quantity, 0)) AS num_refund_items,
                SUM(if(r.return_outcome = 'Exchanges & Shop Now', r.return_item_quantity, 0)) AS num_exchange_items,
                SUM(r.order_item_price * GREATEST(r.order_item_quantity, r.order_shipped_item_quantity) * COALESCE(r.conversion_rate_order_to_shop, 1)) AS total_order_value_shop_currency,
                SUM(r.return_value_cents_shop_currency) / 100 AS total_return_value_shop_currency,
                SUM(r.exchange_from_value_cents_shop_currency) / 100 AS total_exchange_from_value_shop_currency,
                SUM(r.exchange_to_value_cents_shop_currency) / 100 AS total_exchange_to_value_shop_currency,
                SUM(r.shop_now_exchange_value_shop_currency) / 100 AS total_shop_now_exchange_value_shop_currency,
                SUM(IF(r.return_outcome = 'Refund to Original Payment', r.return_value_cents_shop_currency, 0)) / 100 AS total_refund_value_shop_currency,
                SUM(IF(r.return_outcome = 'Gift Cards', r.return_value_cents_shop_currency, 0)) / 100 AS total_gift_card_value_shop_currency,
                CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() as modified_at,
                FARM_FINGERPRINT(CONCAT(
                    COALESCE(r.retailer_moniker, ''),
                    COALESCE(r.shopify_domain, ''),
                    COALESCE(SAFE_CAST(DATE(r.order_date) AS STRING), ''),
                    COALESCE(r.order_checkout_locale, ''),
                    COALESCE(r.order_item_product_id, ''),
                    COALESCE(r.order_item_description, ''),
                    COALESCE(r.order_item_name, ''),
                    COALESCE(r.order_item_sku, ''),
                    COALESCE(r.order_item_vendor, ''),
                    COALESCE(r.order_item_size, ''),
                    COALESCE(r.order_item_color, ''),
                    COALESCE(r.order_item_product_type, ''),
                    COALESCE(r.return_outcome, ''),
                    COALESCE(r.order_item_variant_id, ''),
                    COALESCE(r.order_item_variant_title, '')
                )) AS primary_key_hash
            FROM `narvar-data-lake.return_insights_base.order_item_details` r
            INNER JOIN affected_items a
                ON r.retailer_moniker = a.retailer_moniker
                AND r.shopify_domain = a.shopify_domain
                AND DATE(r.order_date) = DATE(a.order_date)
                AND r.order_item_sku = a.order_item_sku
            GROUP BY
                r.retailer_moniker,
                r.shopify_domain,
                DATE(r.order_date),
                r.order_checkout_locale,
                r.order_item_product_id,
                r.order_item_description,
                r.order_item_name,
                r.order_item_sku,
                r.order_item_vendor,
                r.order_item_size,
                r.order_item_color,
                r.order_item_product_type,
                r.return_outcome,
                r.order_item_variant_id,
                r.order_item_variant_title,
                primary_key_hash
        )
